courtney-1.3 requires perl5 and tcpdump.  perl5 can be ftp'ed from 
ftp.sco.com as /Skunk2/CD-ROM/bin/perl.  tcpdump is part of this distribution.

Note the courtney.pl shell script expects perl to reside in /bin and that
tcpdump is in your PATH.  Edit courtney.pl as necessary.


